short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Dark theme for all of GitHub based on Atom One Dark.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This package will change appearance of all GitHub pages to a dark theme, mostly based on Atom One Dark.

Project forked from poychang/github-dark-theme. it's using Codemirror styles from StylishThemes/GitHub-Dark.
